description:
Join James Gunn with co-hosts Steve Agee (John Economos) and Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) in the official Peacemaker podcast as they break down the Peacemaker Season 2 premiere, “The Ties That Grind.” Special guests Frank Grillo (Rick Flag Sr.) and Sol Rodriguez (Sasha Bordeaux) share exclusive behind-the-scenes stories from the set. Explore Peacemaker’s evolving relationships, get insider details on the explosive new action sequences and discover how John Cena tackled THAT raucous scene. You know what we’re talking about. Hear insights into new DC Universe characters, shocking twists, and the emotional arcs shaping Season 2.
